summary: Listen, Tony did not endanger Peter. As we know, Peter was already being Spider-Man before Tony even met him. All Tony did was...
body: Listen, Tony did not endanger Peter. As we know, Peter was already being Spider-Man before Tony even met him. All Tony did was get him a suit that could help him be safer. He also did NOT give a teenager an “Instant Kill” option. Ned hacked the suit to get rid of everything blocking that. That was obviously for when Peter was a lot older and more responsible. What does endanger underage teenagers, is dropping an airport ramp on them, Steve Rogers. Don’t @ me

summary: Something that I think is really cool in the new Spider Man game is that they made MJ a reporter for the Daily Bugle. I’m really...
body: Something that I think is really cool in the new Spider Man game is that they made MJ a reporter for the Daily Bugle. I’m really liking the concept of having her and Peter working together in some sense so it’s really cool to see her in the front lines side by side with Spider Man and not constantly be the damsel in distress. It’s small but something really refreshing.
